item.description: Experienced Embedded Software Engineer with a demonstrated history of working in the semiconductor industry. Skilled in Matlab, Embedded Systems, Field-Programmable Gate Arrays (FPGA), and Control Theory. Strong information technology professional with a Master’s degree (Ing.) focused on Cybernetics, Control and Measurement from Brno University of Technology.
